        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 23–34. Male of Glyphiulus polytrichus (Golovatch et al., 2011) comb. nov. 23. anterior part of body, dorsal view; 24. same, lateral view; 25. midbody rings, dorsal view; 26. same, lateral view; 27. posterior part of body, dorsal view; 28. same, lateral view; 29. legs I, posterior view; 30. coxosternal processes of legs I, posterior view; 31. anterior gonopods, posterior view; 32. coxite process of anterior gonopod, posterior view; 33. posterior gonopods, anterior view; 34. flagellum of posterior gonopod, anterior view.Abbreviations: csp, coxosternal process; cx, coxite; cxp, coxite process; f, flagellum; s, sternite; t, telopodite. Scale bars: 23–26 = 0.5 mm; 27–29, 31 = 0.2 mm; 30 = 0.05 mm; 32 = 0.4 mm; 33 = 0.1 mm; 34 = 0.04 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4428045/files/figure.png" .

